61253::$$$message_0561_0000_0000$$$::I should take it easy and relax after a meal.[lr]::
61254::$$$message_0561_0000_0001$$$::Brainpower gets diverted to digestion after a meal anyway, and above all, I like having tea after I eat.[lr]::
61255::$$$message_0561_0000_0002$$$::I feel bad for doing this while the other two are washing dishes, but Saber and Sakura seem to be getting along in the kitchen.::
61256::$$$message_0561_0001_0000$$$::They don't have anything in common to talk about, so working on house chores together is building trust.::
61257::$$$message_0561_0002_0000$$$::"Those two get along pretty well, huh?"[lr]::
61258::$$$message_0561_0002_0001$$$::I watch them while I relax in the living room.[lr]::
61259::$$$message_0561_0002_0002$$$::I turn on the TV, which shows the typical daytime programming for housewives.[lr]::
61260::$$$message_0561_0002_0003$$$::I let the atmosphere soothe my body and mind, and simply rest without doing anything else.::
61261::$$$message_0561_0003_0000$$$::After my break, I feel much better.[lr]::
61262::$$$message_0561_0003_0001$$$::My fever seems to have been due to fatigue, so I'm back to normal after resting for half a day.::
61263::$$$message_0561_0004_0000$$$::"Shirou, will you use the rest of the afternoon to train?"[lr]::
61264::$$$message_0561_0004_0001$$$::I nod at Saber.::
61265::$$$message_0561_0005_0000$$$::Even though I've just gotten over an illness, I don't want to waste time.[lr]::
61266::$$$message_0561_0005_0001$$$::I can't improve my magecraft in a few days, but I can work on my combat skills.[lr]::
61267::$$$message_0561_0005_0002$$$::Having Saber train me until dinner should be a good use of my time.::

